
---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Membership | AmicBridge">
  <section style="padding: 3rem 1rem; max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto; text-align: center;">
    <h1 style="font-size: 2rem; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 1rem;">Get Access to Investment Insights</h1>

    <p style="font-size: 1.1rem; line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 2rem;">
      AmicBridge gives you verified, data-driven investment information on crypto and real estate markets.
      To access our <strong>Investment Opportunities</strong> page, you need a membership that unlocks premium insights.
    </p>

    <h2 style="font-size: 1.4rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">Membership Fee</h2>
    <p style="font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: bold;">$49 / One time</p>

    <p style="margin-top: 1rem; font-size: 1.1rem;">
      Once you complete payment, you will receive a secure link and password to access our private Investment page.
    </p>

    <div style="margin-top: 2rem;">
      <a href="https://www.paypal.me/amicbridge" target="_blank" 
         style="background: #0070f3; color: white; padding: 0.9rem 1.8rem; border-radius: 6px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold;">
        Pay Now
      </a>
    </div>

    <p style="margin-top: 1.5rem; font-size: 0.95rem; color: #555;">
      After payment, contact us at <strong>info@amicbridge.com</strong> to get your private access credentials.
    </p>
  </section>
</Layout>
